J. No: 55
No. 75/CF/52.(1)
GOVERNMENT OF INDIA
CABINET SECRETARIAT
New Delhi, the 14th February, 1956.
The undersigned is directed to inform Members of the
Council of Ministers that the following Ministers assumed
office with effect from today, the 14th February, 1956
(12 noon).-
To
1. Shri Raj Bahadur
2. Shri Balwant Nagesh Datar
... Minister in the Ministry
of Communications.
***
68-
Minister in the Ministry
of Home Affairs.
Asciu
(A.S. Gill)
for Secretary to the Cabinet.
All Members of the Council of Ministers.
Copy forwarded to the Secretary to the President/the
Private Secretary to the Vice-President/the Special Assistant
to the Prime Minister/the Principal Private Secretary to the
Prime Minister, for information.
Asenu
(A.S. Gill)
Under Secretary to the Cabinet
Copy forwarded to all Secretaries to the Government of
India/Chairman, Railway Board/Joint Secretary, Planning
Commission, for information.
Copy forwarded to all Kinistries of the Government of
India (including Ministry of Railways)/Deptt. of Parliamentary
Affairs/Planning Commission/Department of Atomic Energy, for
information.
Aseni
-
(.S. Gill)
Under Secretary to the Cabinet.
Copy to Military Ving/Central Statistical Organisation/
Administration Section/Establishment Section/Organisation &
Methods Division/Prime Minister's Secretariat.
